MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 612

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF SAN JUAN ELEMENTARY SCHOOL, A CERTAIN PARCEL OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN BARANGAY SAN JUAN, MUNICIPALITY OF CABAGAN, PROVINCE OF ISABELA, ISLAND OF LUZON

Upon recommendation of the Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources, and by virtue of the powers vested in me by law, I, GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO , President of the Republic of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from entry, sale, disposition or settlement, and reserve for school site purposes of San Juan Elementary School, subject to private rights, if any there be, a certain parcel of land of the public domain situated in Barangay San Juan, Municipality of Cabagan, Province of Isabela, Island of Luzon, which parcel of land is more particularly described as follows:

LOT NO. 973, PLS-834-D

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot No. 973, Pls-834-D) as surveyed for San Juan School Site, situated in Barangay San Juan, Municipality of Cabagan, Province of Isabela, Island of Luzon. Bounded on the NE., along line 1-2 by Lot No. 972; on the SE., along line 2-3 by Lot No. 958; on the SW., along line 3-4 by Lot No. 956, all of Pls-834-D; on the NW., SW., along lines 4-5-6-7-8; on the NW., along lines 8-9-10-11 all by San Juan Creek; and on the NW., along line 11-1 by Road.

Beginning at a point marked “1” on plan being S. 23 deg. 10′ W., 207.70 meters from BLLM No. 1, Pls-834-D, thence:

152.04 m. to point 2;

104.79 m. to point 3;

37.74 m. to point 4;

9.48 m. to point 5;

25.16 m. to point 6;

37.17 m. to point 7;

30.36 m. to point 8;

44.49 m. to point 9;

9.18 m. to point 10;

25.79 m. to point 11;

97.53 m. to point of

beginning, containing an area of NINETEEN THOUSAND TWO HUNDRED THIRTY ONE (19,231) SQUARE METERS , more or less. All point referred to are indicated on the plan and are marked on the ground by P.S. Cyl. Con. Mons. 15 x 40 cms. In diameter. Bearing: True: and that the survey was executed by Geodetic Engineer Santiago G. Perez on May 6, 1963 and was approved on February 29, 1968.

The area covered by the proclamation shall be under the administrative supervision of the Department of Education.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

DONE in the City of Manila, this 20th day of April, in the year of Our Lord, Two Thousand and Four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

